Supplemental Nutrition Assistance Program Integrity
10 Overlay Revolving Fund; creating the Corrections
Transparency Overlay Revolving Fund; identifying
11 funding sources; providing purpose of funds;
providing for noncodification; providing for
12 codification; and providing an effective date.
